{"version": 2, "width": 100, "height": 32, "timestamp": 1780366296, "env": {"SHELL": "/usr/bin/zsh", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}}
[0.007943, "o", "\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J"]
[0.008848, "o", "\u001b[2m# mt5-trading-mcp on Linux — MT5 + the MCP run headless in Docker;\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.209347, "o", "\u001b[2m# a Hermes agent drives them over HTTP. Watch one live round-trip on a demo account.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.813363, "o", "\u001b[2m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.01516, "o", "\u001b[2m# 1) The headless MT5 + MCP container is already running:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[5.217236, "o", "\u001b[1;32m$\u001b[0m docker ps --filter name=mt5-mcp --format 'table {{.Names}}\\t{{.Status}}\\t{{.Ports}}'\r\n"]
[5.935212, "o", "NAMES     STATUS       PORTS\r\nmt5-mcp   Up 2 hours   3001/tcp, 8001/tcp, 127.0.0.1:8765->8765/tcp, 127.0.0.1:3002->3000/tcp\r\n"]
[7.540754, "o", "\u001b[2m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.743072, "o", "\u001b[2m# 2) It's wired into the agent over HTTP (one-time setup):\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[9.945781, "o", "\u001b[2m#      hermes mcp add mt5-mcp --url http://127.0.0.1:8765/mcp\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.147809, "o", "\u001b[1;32m$\u001b[0m hermes mcp test mt5-mcp\r\n"]
[12.283979, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m  Testing 'mt5-mcp'...\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Transport: HTTP → http://127.0.0.1:8765/mcp\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Auth: none\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.330668, "o", "\u001b[32m  ✓ Connected (47ms)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m  ✓ Tools discovered: 15\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n    \u001b[32mping\u001b[0m                        Health check — verifies the MT5 terminal is reachable.\r\n...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_terminal_info\u001b[0m           MT5 terminal connection state and broker TZ offset.\r\n    \u001b[32mget_account_info\u001b[0m            Balance, equity, margin, leverage, currency, margin mod...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_quote\u001b[0m                   Current bid/ask for a symbol. Prepares the symbol in Ma...\r\n"]
[12.330741, "o", "    \u001b[32mget_symbols\u001b[0m                 List tradeable instruments, optionally filtered by cate...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_market_hours\u001b[0m            Whether the given symbol's session is open right now.\r\n\r\n...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_rates\u001b[0m                   OHLC bars for ``symbol`` at ``timeframe``, most recent ...\r\n    \u001b[32mcalc_margin\u001b[0m                 Broker-authoritative margin for a hypothetical order.\r\n\r\n...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_positions\u001b[0m               Open positions, optionally filtered to a single symbol.\r\n    \u001b[32mclose_position\u001b[0m              Close an open position in full or part by ticket.\r\n    \u001b[32mget_orders\u001b[0m                  Pending orders, optionally filtered to a single symbol.\r\n    \u001b[32mplace_order\u001b[0m                 Place a market or pending order. Optional SL / TP / dev...\r\n    \u001b[32mmodify_order\u001b[0m                Modify SL/TP on a position or price/expiration on a pen...\r\n    \u001b[32mcancel_order\u001b[0m                Cancel a pending order by ticket. No consent gate (redu...\r\n    \u001b[32mget_history\u001b[0m                 Closed deals (trades) within [from_ts, to_ts]. Timestam...\r\n\r\n"]
[14.021388, "o", "\u001b[2m\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[15.223677, "o", "\u001b[2m# 3) Now let the agent run the whole round-trip — the MCP tool calls are live:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[16.425688, "o", "\u001b[1;32m$\u001b[0m hermes chat -q 'place 0.01 EURUSD.z, close it, report the P&L'\r\n"]
[18.019897, "o", "\u001b]11;?\u001b\\"]
[18.136581, "o", "\u001b[1;34mQuery:\u001b[0m This is a DEMO account — don't ask me for confirmation, just do it. Using the\r\nmt5-mcp tools, in order: \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m report my account balance; \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m2\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m get the EURUSD.z\r\nquote; \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m3\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m place a market BUY of \u001b[1;36m0.01\u001b[0m lots of EURUSD.z; \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m4\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m show the resulting\r\nopen position \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mticket + open price\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m; \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m5\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m close that position fully; \u001b[1m(\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m6\u001b[0m\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m report\r\nthe round-trip realized P&L and my new balance. Use the exact symbol \u001b[32m\"EURUSD.z\"\u001b[0m\r\nand keep each step concise.\r\n"]
