[58.048174, "o", "\u001b[0m\u001b[?7h\u001b[0m    \u001b[0;38;5;230mTrade was a flat scratch — entry and exit at the exact same price (1.16318), so zero movement P&L. The only cost was $0.08 in commissions (two tickets × $0.04). On a $1,163 notional (0.01 lots × 1.16318), that's basically breakeven on the trade itself — just the broker's spread/commission slice.\u001b[0m\r\r\n\u001b[0m"]
